description: The General is Noon Gunâ€™s 18-Pounder Session IPA (India Pale Ale) alcohol-free beer twin. Brewed the same way, born the same way. Thus far, no one has been able to tell the difference between the sibling variants. Awarded Double Gold at the Aurora International Taste Challenge.

name: Noughty Rouge Syrah Non-Alcoholic Wine
description: Noughty Rouge Shiraz De-Alcoholised Wine combines red fruit flavours with a little spice, upheld by elegant texture, silky tannins and well-balanced acidity.

name: Absolute Zero Dry Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Wine
description: Absolute Zero Dry is a delicious non-alcoholic champagne with tiny festive bubbles, crisp tropical flavours on the palate and well balanced with a smooth finish. After vinification this premium sparkling wine was de-alcoholised with the latest spinning cone technology.

name: Inah Cabernet Sauvignon Superior Grape Juice
description: Distinctive Cabernet Sauvignon flavours reminiscent of black berry and ripe plums enhanced with oak in this all natural, premium 100% alcohol-free Grape Juice. Enjoy with a meal or on its own. Pairs beautifully with red meats, venison and poultry. Inah is a Halaal certified product.

name: Inah Shiraz Superior Grape Juice
description: Distinctive Shiraz flavours reminiscent of sweet berries and fruit in this 100% alcohol-free Grape Juice. Through Inah's innovative Flash Dente system, grapes are momentarily heated and flashed cooled to extract their natural colours and flavours. Enjoy with a meal or on its own. Inah is a Halaal certified product.

name: Babylonstoren Alcohol-Free Sparkling Grape Juice
description: A light, crisp, Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Grape Juice that is fruit driven and juicy. Refreshing with lovely guava, pineapple and winter melon flavours, rounded off with a hint of fresh gooseberries and packham pear undertones.

name: Inah Merlot Superior Grape Juice
description: A premium 100% alcohol-free Grape Juice with distinctive Merlot flavours reminiscent of strawberry and black current. Enjoy with a meal or on its own. Pairs beautifully with red meats, venison and poultry. Inah is a Halaal certified product.

name: Inah Rossore Sparkling Grape Juice
description: Inah Rossore is a 100% natural sparkling grape juice with a crisp, fresh, sparkling flavor. Rossore can be enjoyed all year around. Best served chilled and refrigerate once opened. Contains no artificial colorants or preservatives. Rossore is a Halaal certified product.
